&#xD;
When I came across this recipe .. I saw something .. something.. I thought I had long but forgotten.. &#xD;
&#xD;
I gathered up my ingredients.. drove to my mothers house.. and made that bitch mix up my shit.&#xD;
&#xD;
After 3 painstakingly long hours. It was finally ready..&#xD;
&#xD;
I filled up my electronic cigarette, and subsequently my lungs with this vapour ..&#xD;
&#xD;
A tear ..&#xD;
&#xD;
A tear rolled down my cheek ..&#xD;
